<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10441231>
    dc:description "FIGURE 1. Forewing line drawings of seven species from Poljanka. A, Poljanka curticapillata Lü, Luo & Yao, sp. nov. B, Poljanka strigosa Yang et al., 2013. C, Poljanka hirsuta Yang et al., 2012. D, Poljanka ventriculosa Becker-Migdisova, 1985. E, Poljanka kukalovae Becker-Migdisova, 1985. F, Poljanka sharovi Becker-Migdisova, 1985. G, Poljanka shurabensis Becker-Migdisova, 1985. Scale bars = 1 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10441231/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

